comments: Siakam (TOR) and Green (CHI) briefly engage and disengage in the post before the pass.
Anunoby (TOR) makes marginal contact to Vucevic's (CHI) body before the pick.
Vucevic (CHI) extends his arm slightly and makes marginal contact with Siakam (TOR) on the perimeter.
Vucevic (CHI) dislodges Banton (TOR) from his position during the rebound.
Dosunmu (CHI) makes incidental contact with Boucher's (TOR) hand after the ball has been tipped out during the rebound.
Banton (TOR) holds Vucevic's (CHI) arm and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
After the rebound, DeRozan (CHI) takes a controlled dribble, gathers the ball by pinning it against his body, and restarts his dribble.
Banton (TOR) makes clean contact with the ball prior to any incidental arm contact with Vucevic (CHI) on the pass.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: LaVine (CHI) loses the ball out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to TOR.
LaVine (CHI) is established in Anunoby's (TOR) path when incidental body contact occurs on the perimeter.
Green (CHI) is moving alongside Siakam's (TOR) path when he collapses his forearm before moving to a vertical position, causing marginal contact to occur on the driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) is moving alongside DeRozan's (CHI) path when incidental contact occurs on the perimeter.
Boucher (TOR) legally contests Vucevic's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
DeRozan (CHI) legally contests Barnes' (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) reaches across DeRozan's (TOR) body and legally contacts the ball.
Barnes (TOR) reaches across DeRozan's (CHI) body and legally contacts the ball.
